data.description: Only a few blocks from Hopkinton's downtown common...a hidden gem on 7 acres. Stroll down winding, scenic driveway & pass the pond to your contemporary home w breathtaking grounds. Four bedroom, 3.5 bath, 11 room residence w 7-9 garage bays. In 2006, the home was gutted to studs & meticulously renovated w high quality finishes throughout. This one of a kind home is ideal for entertaining & offers comfortable living, cozy gathering areas & the perfect oasis for a great work/life balance. Vaulted living/music room w skylights opens to family room with walls of windows, wood burning fireplace & office area. Upstairs 4 bedrooms, 3 baths, loft & laundry. GAS HEAT. Cozy up to a good book on the huge screened deck listening to and enjoying nature in your yard. Two story garage/barn, great for storage of cars, a workshop, an equestrian facility & more. Sidewalks lead to State's #1 schools (per Niche). 495/90/Commuter rails minutes away. Don't let this rare opportunity pass you by!
